{"tid":2501100,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"針對中俄  美國通過規定廣播機構須標明外國政府贊助節目","createTime":"2021-04-23T06:40:25.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-23T06:57:54.000Z","uid":227801,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"6e1a9e8b802403386c5d0f1503104b3a8cc2a700","tid":2501100,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T06:40:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/international/2388575\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Finternational%2F2388575&d=9fgUEJ%2BH4pM5xz2q5iffzhnxOJLX742lx1SCoot1iYY%3D&h=a20a2b44\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/international/2388575</a><br />\n發佈時間 2021-04-23 13:46&nbsp;最後更新時間 2021-04-23 13:45<br />\n<br />\n美國聯邦通訊委員會通過新規定，要求廣播機構須公布節目是否獲外國政府贊助或提供內容。委員會聲明指，新規定增加透明度，令觀眾和聽眾注意到是否有外國政府或相關代表透過大氣電波進行游說工作。委員會代理主席指，有報告顯示外國政府在全美國都有購買廣播時段，包括中國和俄羅斯政府，日後在節目播出時需要作出相關聲明，並在公開訊息中披露。<br />\n全美廣播事業者聯盟表示，認同聯邦通訊委員會的加強披露相關訊息的目標，但擔心會對廣播機構造成負擔。"},{"pid":"c3f9b557352a3766fdc5ac5c00cc58be9713c8ac","tid":2501100,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T06:44:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/discover.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2d36fa0fc1fea83bf34ed23a5a8f9276cab8539","tid":2501100,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T06:49:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/stretching.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6c4908382c267effb649d81f22c1e8383928722","tid":2501100,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T06:57:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/stretching.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}